{"tid":26751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人組團來港清潔海灘 自費逾30萬 執550公斤垃圾","createTime":"2016-12-07T02:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T07:05:19.000Z","uid":8968,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af7a399f466475f931a4db5a317b1e4d51cfc5f5","tid":26751,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:02:52.000Z","msg":"本港今年暑假受內地暴雨影響，令大量垃圾湧港，香港海灘突變成垃圾灘。居住於日本沖繩的鈴木博將（HIROMASA SUZUKI），8月時曾特意飛來香港執垃圾。不過，他近日又再次訪港，今次更組團逾30位日本人一起到海灘進行大掃除。<br />\n<br />\n據鈴木博將早前在facebook指，由上月底開始會到世界各地清潔海灘，第一站就是香港，呼籲日本人參與；香港站定於11月25至29日，旅程五日四夜，每人需自費逾萬元來港，分別大嶼山大浪灣海灘和南丫島蘆鬚城海灘執垃圾，最終清理約552公斤的垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n今年31歲的鈴木博將，是日本環保組織Open Earth成員，自2013年起，幾乎每日在沖繩海灘執垃圾。他憶述日本西岸海灘常有垃圾從中國和韓國飄來，辛勞一日清潔後，垃圾又再飄至，似永無休止，自己有時也感到挫敗，但仍堅持下去，至今累計清理逾6噸垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161207&amp;guid=56011722&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161207%26guid%3D56011722%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=MA7QpwznWU4lNDv43ySS%2F5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=92420f1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161207%26guid%3D56011722%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=fd41cee4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161207&amp;guid=56011722&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"c25f5fd450c75f78b67000bf873767dbf2d472bf","tid":26751,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9faa0ce579e2374d8088224bc618947cd2a1c6","tid":26751,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T02:11:15.000Z","msg":"又係中